{"tid":1266610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近排大家好似好負面","createTime":"2019-06-29T14:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:15:22.000Z","uid":82432,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd42a0a3ef3ec3bc6e94036c6a70c8db751545bd","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"發覺近排大家好負面 可能因為大家都用左好多體力同心力行出黎抗爭 有啲人甚至拎埋自己嘅前途同自由較飛 而家仲坐緊監<br />\n<br />\n但換黎嘅<br />\n<br />\n係政府乜撚都冇回應 一如既往做緊香港之恥 冇撤回逃犯 冇釋放義士 冇追究狗嘅責任 林奠仲係做緊所謂嘅特首 冇一個我地嘅訴求係政府有做到 <br />\n<br />\n我自問遊行上街都有去齊 係嗰隻會關心 會行動的人但唔敢勇武 唔敢衝 12號狗啲催淚彈都嚇撚到我仆街嘅懦弱之人 不過我都會幫手大嗌口號 幫手搬物資上前線 幫手叫人出 貢獻唔多 但起碼叫有出力<br />\n<br />\n然後到呢幾日 感覺好似我抗爭嘅火 熄左一部份 一黎抗爭嘅聲音好似弱左 二黎又有好多on9野發生 eg 狗扮同打示威者 cctvb垃圾報道 政府各種足球比賽等等 都打擊緊我嘅意志力同埋想繼續抗爭嘅意慾<br />\n<br />\n我都想放棄 但係 每當我諗起 坐緊監嘅義士 犧牲左嘅年輕人（今晚又多左個...）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一班勇武嘅義士 我就知道我唔可以放棄 我都要繼續行出黎 盡自己能力範圍幫手 可能一個唔多 但我地香港700萬人 多你一個其實好多！<br />\n<br />\n所以！我呼籲同我一樣諗法或者同我類似嘅人 1/7 記得出黎！同埋叫埋其他朋友出黎 我地唔可以就咁放棄 我地要俾班撚樣睇 香港唔係咁撚好恰 出到黎唔一定要勇武要點 我地要嘅係俾全世界見到我地香港團結一致 永不放棄！<br />\n<br />\n我知道有好多分化撚 會話香港玩完啦 啲人咁善忘 做乜都冇用 香港遲早回歸中國做香港市乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n但係！<br />\n<br />\n就算香港真係命數已盡 我地都有責任 企出黎！為我地嘅香港發聲！因為呢一個唔係一個做左會成功定失敗嘅問題 而係一個我地應該同必須要盡嘅責任！香港人仍需加油！<br />\n<br />\n所以 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1/7 香港人 出黎吧</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申 冇野做好悶諗出黎"},{"pid":"298149e3a886a3feb8fb4808f9b194a492a48a60","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"再利申 第一次出po 補文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ST9WxAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FST9WxAH.png&h=b470c025&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c382b0bda28183d218e59a5f8ebc281ee8d8348a","tid":1266610,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"[長文]求下大家唔好自殺，有梁先生真係夠啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266479</a>"},{"pid":"ea4d3a7baa93a968403ee1da750433dc7464817b","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"35dcff219fc7966e654575eda395d893ab19594a","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bd1537fe957b35f39bb73f36266b63f322d8f8f0","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8d31008543bf2ec2847e69298fe6d895cf18f46","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8b62f21c02594bc37aaa14f1f834400816c6ec","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954a0404e27c34e85d6fd8133eb30df0e5a8146e","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c6409bc959a030f2b54982b26c10e173d4cc31","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766813e3b522e7465255878aa2db91f4d7ecaac8","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e59422801b5aff085db935c53f643d0143a801f","tid":1266610,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}